@returns(none)
def ensure_viewport()
</code></synopsis>
<p>Ensures that the GL viewport is updated with the current
stage window size.</p><p>This function will queue a redraw of @stage.</p><p>This function should not be called by applications; it is used
when embedding a <link xref="Clutter.Stage">Clutter.Stage</link> into a toolkit with another
windowing system, like GTK+.</p>

